      },
      "say": "在鐵必制的邀約下，來到了港區附近的某處高台",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "百忙之中能抽身陪我，實在是榮幸。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "對了，今天有個東西，想讓你陪我一起看。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
