        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "北極星？",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "say": "鐵必制用手指向了天空",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "嗯，Polarstern。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "每當看見這顆星星，我就會想起那個時候，作為“存在艦隊”而一直待在那個港口的自己。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "寒冷，孤獨，這些我早已視為無物。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "最後，什麼也做不了，只能在港口絕望地看著天空，迎來自己的終局。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "很可笑吧，這樣的結局。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "……",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "但是，現在不一樣了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "與人交流時的愉快，有人陪伴時的心臟的鼓動……這些心情，充滿了溫暖，像是要把所有寒冷與孤獨融化一般燃燒著。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "“孤獨的北方女王”，已經不再孤獨了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "如果，夢中的“另一個我”，能像現在這樣的話就好了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "啊啊，我感覺有點累了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
